Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------- ED ---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:15.04,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are tossed by the waves of pain and tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:18.74,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tossed into the fray tossed by various fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:22.49,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up your brain!Flashed in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.77,0:22:25.07,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a burst of sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.14,0:22:31.23,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“谛め”がくれた 安楽沈滞の世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.59,0:22:37.51,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつからだっただろう？ふいに輝き始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.63,0:22:40.71,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,変わらずにいてと愿うこと-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.85,0:22:44.42,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,変わりゆく时に生きる仆ら-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.52,0:22:47.60,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の声を…言い得ぬ梦を…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.66,0:22:51.61,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君と繋がった空へ　响かせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.58,0:22:55.88,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっと强く…この両手で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.99,0:22:59.20,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙全て振り払えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.28,0:23:02.47,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“今度こそは…”つぶやく今と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:05.64,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤さえも无駄にしない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.82,0:23:08.94,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっと早く…君のもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.13,0:23:12.32,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,たとえ羽が千切れようとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.43,0:23:15.59,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪む世界　走り抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.69,0:23:18.85,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覚のその向こうへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:24.36,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“真実”と　加速してく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:15.04,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are tossed by the waves of pain and tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:18.74,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tossed into the fray tossed by various fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:22.49,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up your brain!Flashed in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.77,0:22:25.07,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a burst of sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.14,0:22:31.23,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“放弃”所带给我的 安乐但停滞的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.59,0:22:37.51,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知从什么时候开始  突然间开始变得闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.63,0:22:40.71,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈望永恒不变的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.85,0:22:44.42,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不断改变地世界生存的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.52,0:22:47.60,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心声…无法说出梦想…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.66,0:22:51.61,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响彻着 这与你相连的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.58,0:22:55.88,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果更用力地…用你的双手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.99,0:22:59.20,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我挥去所有的泪水的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.28,0:23:02.47,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将永不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:05.64,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这些伤痕也不会让它白费
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.82,0:23:08.94,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更快地 前往你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.13,0:23:12.32,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这双翅膀被撕裂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.43,0:23:15.59,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要奔出 这扭曲的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.69,0:23:18.85,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着我所感受到的彼方前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:24.36,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我的“真实”去加速
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------- ED ---------------------
